Functional Requirements:

User registration and login system
Search and booking of cabs based on availability, location, and time
Integration with payment gateway to process payments
Tracking of booked cabs in real-time
Cancellation of booked cabs
Availability of different types of cabs based on user requirements
Rating and review system for both users and drivers
Option to schedule future bookings
Notification system for booking confirmation, ride updates, and payment confirmation
User profile management system to view and edit personal information
Non-Functional Requirements:

Security: The system must ensure the privacy and security of user information and payment details.
Performance: The system should be responsive and able to handle multiple requests simultaneously, ensuring fast loading and response times.
Reliability: The system must ensure that all bookings are processed accurately and reliably, with minimal downtime or errors.
Scalability: The system should be able to scale up to handle an increasing number of users and bookings.
User-friendly: The system should be easy to use, with a simple and intuitive interface.
Compatibility: The system should be compatible with different operating systems and devices.
Availability: The system should be available 24/7, with minimal downtime for maintenance and updates.
Accuracy: The system should ensure that all information, including pricing and availability of cabs, is accurate and up-to-date.
